  <section>
    <h2>Why Most Recruitment Agencies Fall Short</h2>
    <p>Traditional recruitment firms often rely on outdated methods: mass job postings, generic databases, and volume-based placements. This leads to longer time-to-hire, mismatched candidates, and high turnover — costing businesses time and money.</p>
    <p>Required Hire takes a radically different approach — one built for today's competitive talent landscape.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Key Ways Required Hire Stands Out from the Competition</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Deep Industry Specialization</strong> — Unlike generalist agencies, we focus on niche sectors, giving us insider knowledge of market trends, salary benchmarks, and hidden talent pools competitors simply don't access.</li>
      <li><strong>Proactive Talent Pipelining</strong> — We don't wait for openings. We build exclusive talent communities year-round, so top candidates are ready when you need them — slashing time-to-fill by up to 50% compared to reactive competitors.</li>
      <li><strong>Personalized, Human-Centered Matching</strong> — Beyond resumes, we evaluate cultural fit, growth potential, and long-term value. Generic agencies push volume; we prioritize quality hires that stay and thrive.</li>
      <li><strong>Transparent & Data-Driven Process</strong> — You get real metrics: time-to-hire, retention rates, candidate satisfaction scores. Most competitors hide behind vague promises — we prove results with transparency.</li>
      <li><strong>Speed Without Sacrificing Quality</strong> — Advanced sourcing tools + experienced consultants deliver shortlists in days, not weeks, while maintaining rigorous vetting other agencies skip.</li>
      <li><strong>Strategic Partnership Mindset</strong> — We're not just a vendor filling seats. We act as an extension of your HR team — offering employer branding advice, market insights, and retention strategies competitors rarely provide.</li>
      <li><strong>Guaranteed Long-Term Fit</strong> — Our replacement guarantee and post-placement support go far beyond the industry standard, ensuring your investment in talent truly pays off.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

